Oops Britney Spears might have just done it again! RadarOnline.com has obtained a leaked sex tape of the singer.

Radar reportedly has seen the footage of the 32-year-old topless and smoking what could be a joint.

A source revealed she’s “horrified this is happening to her after everything that she’s been through.”

And added, “She’s totally mortified.”

Watch the video above and don’t forget to subscribe to our YouTube Channel!
title: Britney Spears ‘Mortified’ About Leaked Sex Tape
